The paper discusses machine learning methods for learning dictionaries of natural image patches, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses optimization methods for solving inverse problems, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Finally, the paper discusses structured sparsity, which is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.IT, cs.NA, and cs.SI.
